   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "markdown",
   "metadata": {},
   "source": [
    "## Step 5 — Run the pipeline\n",
    "\n",
    "Choose one mode and run that cell.  \n",
    "On first run the autoencoders train (~600 epochs × 5 datasets). Subsequent runs skip that and load cached models.\n",
    "\n",
    "| Mode | What it does |\n",
    "|------|--------------|\n",
    "| `XGBoost` | 4-fold CV XGBoost ensemble (recommended starting point) |\n",
    "| `RandomForest` | 4-fold CV Random Forest ensemble |\n",
    "| `DNN_Classifier` | 4-fold CV MLP ensemble |\n",
    "| `Binary_Classifier` | Threshold-based anomaly detection (only when `ONLY_REGULAR=True`) |"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "code",
   "execution_count": null,
   "metadata": {},
   "outputs": [],
   "source": [
    "from src.pipeline import main\n",
    "main(mode='XGBoost')"
   ]
